#### PR description:

Updated Phase2 L1 CaloJet/Tau code from CMSSW_10_5_0_pre1 release to new data formats in more recent release and added minimum code necessary to produce CaloJets/Taus (L1Trigger/L1CaloTrigger/).

Same as https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/33612 but I made a github mistake in the other PR, which is closed now.

Same as https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/33612

title: L1 phase 2: produce CaloJet/Tau (corrected version)
